oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Union captain's shoulder knots
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Shoulder knots from a uniform belonging to Capt. James E. White, 12th Ind. Lt. Arty., USA. Capt. White was the last commander of Ft. Negley.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Tennessee State Library and Archives, Nashville, Davidson County, Tennessee
